Class AdminController

java.lang.Object
spss.project.backend.user.admin.AdminController
@RestController @CrossOrigin(origins="http://127.0.0.1:3000") @RequestMapping("admin") public class AdminController extends Object
Handles all requests related to the system's administrators.
